data.text:
A young woman, played by Katerina Golubeva, arrives by helicopter in the snow-covered and God-forsaken part of Siberia where the Tofalars live. They are an Asian people that was still nomadic at the turn of the century. The people were forced to settle down, but they still live in their houses as if they were nomads.
